Conte: 我非常尊重球會，球會會作出最好既決定，而我會係第一個人接受呢個決定。經過呢兩個球季後，我會永遠愛上呢種顏色、球迷以及呢間球會。<br />
<br />
I have great respect for my club and they will make the best decision and I am the first to accept the decision. After these two seasons I will always love this colour, the fans and this club. If my future must be in a different way.&rdquo;

